{"tid":1981560,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶4月8日] 交易員以一萬美元買入紐約原油看跌期權至每桶0.5美元","createTime":"2020-04-20T17:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T18:10:26.000Z","uid":47208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1216f26e0b8e3f25b8b65bc307fa17c7e811fc11","tid":1981560,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:39:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200408/LVRQKGC7AKSPGR2HEVDSCTTHRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200408%2FLVRQKGC7AKSPGR2HEVDSCTTHRI%2F&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=f6da4485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200408%2FLVRQKGC7AKSPGR2HEVDSCTTHRI%2F&h=890bae56\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200408/LVRQKGC7AKSPGR2HEVDSCTTHRI/</a><br />\n<br />\n4月8日新聞：<br />\n紐約期油年初至今跌56%，雖然市場對油價前景感憂慮，但跌破每桶一美元似是遙不可及。<span style=\"color: orange;\">《彭博》報道，一名交易員以一萬美元買入1,000手看跌期權，押注紐約原油會跌至每桶0.5美元。</span>另外，交易員們已開始大量買入可從極端低價中獲利的合約，10美元或以下的看跌期權規模最近幾周顯著增加，目前持倉數量超過50,000手，大部份為在過去一個月增長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論今日5月期油結算時去唔去到0.5美元<br />\n呢個大膽既人真係神之操作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然6月期油仲係20美元以上<br />\n但想像唔到今次個差價竟然可以去到咁遠"},{"pid":"2566312fc152ec369ca2d70908e84d149721173a","tid":1981560,"uid":110864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"世界變了"},{"pid":"af2f41866ee065f859b5cdc63c1115b64449edb5","tid":1981560,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:45:28.000Z","msg":"痴撚線勁人"},{"pid":"51052d2ae2ece8b56da93515411de4315e807d34","tid":1981560,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:50:34.000Z","msg":"-6啫<br />\n幾十萬薪家拎七萬嚟賭"},{"pid":"1608be11e36e513cb62ed3f2cc150f5389b2cfe4","tid":1981560,"uid":1983,"like":0,